    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115040/extras/1a844ac3afe851cb54b80a6f5039cf58.poster.avif?t=1769114154\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115040/extras/1a844ac3afe851cb54b80a6f5039cf58.webm?t=1769114154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115040/extras/1a844ac3afe851cb54b80a6f5039cf58.mp4?t=1769114154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你扮演的霍华德是一个急于逃跑的人，但他周围的世界已经扭曲得面目全非。他的旅程将穿越奇异而令人不安的地方，到处都是怪诞的生物和奇怪的人物。当他发现自己在这个噩梦般的现实中扮演的角色时，逃跑显然比他想象的要困难得多。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115040/extras/4c85b253609ceee0e0fa203b4330ee2d.poster.avif?t=1769114154\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115040/extras/4c85b253609ceee0e0fa203b4330ee2d.webm?t=1769114154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115040/extras/4c85b253609ceee0e0fa203b4330ee2d.mp4?t=1769114154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身临其境的第一人称恐怖游戏，扣人心弦的谜题  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧张的解谜和心理恐怖元素  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满令人不安遭遇的深沉氛围世界  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面恐怖，有时唯一的生存之道就是反击</p></li></ul>",
